{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Screen.orientation","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen_Orientation_API\">Screen Orientation API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availHeight\"><code>availHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availLeft\"><code>availLeft</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availTop\"><code>availTop</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/availWidth\"><code>availWidth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/colorDepth\"><code>colorDepth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/left\"><code>left</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozBrightness\"><code>mozBrightness</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozEnabled\"><code>mozEnabled</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>orientation</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/pixelDepth\"><code>pixelDepth</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event\"><code>Screen: orientationchange event</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/top\"><code>top</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/lockOrientation\"><code>lockOrientation()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/unlockOrientation\"><code>unlockOrientation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Screen Orientation API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>Screen.orientation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>orientation</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a> インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティで、現在の画面の向きを返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>orientation</var> = window.screen.orientation;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>画面の向きを表す <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> のインスタンスです。</p>\n\n<p>なお、古い接頭辞付きのものは <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> で <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation/type\"><code>ScreenOrientation.type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> と同等のものを返していました。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> orientation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>msOrientation <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mozOrientation <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>orientation <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>orientation <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"landscape-primary\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"良い感じですね。\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>orientation <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"landscape-secondary\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"うーん…。画面が上下逆です！\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>orientation <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"portrait-secondary\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> orientation <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"portrait-primary\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"うーん…。スクリーンを横向きにした方がいいですよ\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>orientation <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"このブラウザーは orientation API に対応していません :(\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/screen-orientation/#dom-screen-orientation\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Screen Orientation API<br><small lang=\"ja\">orientation の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Screen.orientation","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ScreenOrientation\"><code>ScreenOrientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientat